      "description": "Available now is an exceptional example of the A80 chassis, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. This unit remains in factory-stock configuration, retaining its sequential turbo setup and original intercooler piping. Power is delivered through the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is perfectly preserved with original double-wishbone components, and the four-piston front calipers provide firm, fade-free braking. The exterior showcases original paint depth with zero oxidation, while the cabin maintains its driver-centric ergonomics with pristine upholstery and fully functional instrumentation. Mechanically flawless with a documented service history, this is a turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
